                    digitally enabled methodology could in the future allow syndicated studies on very large cohorts.
                </p>
                <button class="cta-primary-1"><a class="text-decoration-none text-white" href="{{ path('studies_and_services') }}">Read more</a></button>
            </div>
            <div id="radio_bar_right" class="col">
